&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;全省传达学习贯彻习近平总书记视察广东和出席第十五届全国运动会开幕式重要讲话重要指示精神干部大会召开&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>粤港澳大湾区常识</title><link>https://tyd2000.github.io/posts/%E7%B2%A4%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%B9%BE%E5%8C%BA%E5%B8%B8%E8%AF%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Nov 2025 10:26:25 +0800</pubDate><author>tanyaodan@qq.com (t0ur1st)</author><guid>https://tyd2000.github.io/posts/%E7%B2%A4%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%B9%BE%E5%8C%BA%E5%B8%B8%E8%AF%86/</guid><description>&lt;h3 class="heading-element" id="名词解释"&gt;&lt;span&gt;名词解释&lt;/span&gt;
